---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";

const title = "About Nutri Swapper — The Macro & Calorie Swap Calculator";
const description =
  "Learn about Nutri Swapper, a free zero-login macro and calorie density swap calculator built for fast, real-world ingredient substitutions in the kitchen and gym.";
---

<Layout title={title} description={description} path="/about" localized={false}>
  <article class="mx-auto max-w-[760px] px-4 py-16 sm:px-6 sm:py-24">
    <p class="font-mono text-xs uppercase tracking-wider text-mute">// About</p>
    <h1 class="mt-3 text-4xl font-semibold tracking-[-2px] text-ink sm:text-5xl">
      About Nutri Swapper
    </h1>

    <div class="mt-6 space-y-5 text-body leading-relaxed">
      <p>
        <strong class="text-ink">Nutri Swapper</strong> is a free macro and
        calorie density swap calculator with a single, focused job: telling you
        the exact weight of a substitute ingredient that matches the protein or
        calories of the food you ran out of. No accounts, no onboarding, no
        clutter — just an instant answer when you need it.
      </p>

      <h2 class="pt-4 text-xl font-semibold tracking-[-0.6px] text-ink">
        Why we built it
      </h2>
      <p>
        Most nutrition tools are built to log an entire day of eating. They make
        you sign up, sit through onboarding, and load heavy pages that crawl on
        mobile — the exact moment you're standing in the kitchen mid-recipe or
        planning a meal at the gym. We wanted the opposite: a tool that does one
        thing brilliantly and disappears. Nutri Swapper loads in under a second,
        works without a login, and answers “what weight of this equals that?”
        before a bloated app would finish loading.
      </p>

      <h2 class="pt-4 text-xl font-semibold tracking-[-0.6px] text-ink">
        How it works
      </h2>
      <p>
        Every food in our database stores its macros per 100 grams. You enter the
        weight of what you have, choose a substitute, and pick whether to keep
        protein or calories constant. Nutri Swapper solves for the substitute's
        weight and shows a side-by-side macro breakdown so you can see exactly
        what the swap costs or saves you — extra calories on a protein swap, or a
        shift in protein on a calorie swap.
      </p>

      <h2 class="pt-4 text-xl font-semibold tracking-[-0.6px] text-ink">
        Who it's for
      </h2>
      <p>
        Lifters and dieters keeping protein on target, meal-preppers cooking
        around the pantry, and home cooks substituting one ingredient for another
        without wrecking a day's totals. The database covers 40+ common fitness
        and kitchen staples, and popular swaps each have a dedicated page with the
        calculator pre-loaded.
      </p>

      <p class="pt-2">
        Have a suggestion or spotted a number that looks off?
        <a class="text-link hover:underline" href="/contact">Get in touch</a> — or
        jump straight back to the
        <a class="text-link hover:underline" href="/">swap calculator</a>.
      </p>
    </div>
  </article>
</Layout>
